# 🏈 Park Orchards FC & NC — Relationship Cheatsheet

> Tổng hợp tất cả relationships giữa Metaobjects, Metafields, Products, Blogs trong Shopify store.

---

## Relationship Diagram

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "Term Metaobjects (Taxonomy)"
        CS["club_sport"]
        CD["club_division"]
        CG["club_grade"]
        SS["sponsor_scope"]
        ST["sponsor_tier"]
        CPG["club_people_group"]
        MC["membership_category"]
    end

    subgraph "Main Metaobjects"
        CT["club_team"]
        PP["player_profile"]
        CSP["club_sponsor"]
        CP["club_person"]
        MT["membership_type"]
    end

    subgraph "Shopify Native"
        PROD["Product (Membership/Merch)"]
        ART["Article (Events blog)"]
        BLOG_N["Blog: News"]
        BLOG_E["Blog: Events"]
        COLL["Collections"]
    end

    CT -->|sport| CS
    CT -->|division| CD
    CT -->|grade| CG

    PP -->|team| CT

    CSP -->|scope| SS
    CSP -->|tier| ST
    CSP -->|sponsored_player| PP

    CP -->|group| CPG

    MT -->|category| MC
    MT -->|linked_product| PROD

    ART -->|event.related_team| CT

    PROD -.->|membership.* metafields| PROD
    BLOG_E -->|contains| ART
```

---

## 1. Term Metaobjects (Taxonomy Layer)

Các metaobject dùng như taxonomy/terms — được reference bởi các metaobject chính.

| # | Metaobject Type | Fields | Entries | Được dùng bởi |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | `club_sport` | name, sort_order | Football, Netball | `club_team.sport` |
| 2 | `club_division` | name, sort_order | Men, Women | `club_team.division` |
| 3 | `club_grade` | name, sort_order | Seniors, Reserves, Under 19 | `club_team.grade` |
| 4 | `sponsor_scope` | name, sort_order | Club Sponsor, Player Sponsor | `club_sponsor.scope` |
| 5 | `sponsor_tier` | name, sort_order, badge_label | Gold, Silver, Jumper, Community Partner | `club_sponsor.tier` |
| 6 | `club_people_group` | name, sort_order | Committee, Support, Volunteers, Community | `club_person.group` |
| 7 | `membership_category` | name, sort_order | Player, Social, Premium, Honorary | `membership_type.category` |

---

## 2. Main Metaobjects & Their References

### 🏟️ `club_team` — Trục chính, kết nối 3 terms

| Field | Type | References → |
|---|---|---|
| team_name | `single_line_text_field` | — |
| **sport** | `metaobject_reference` | → **`club_sport`** |
| **division** | `metaobject_reference` | → **`club_division`** |
| **grade** | `metaobject_reference` | → **`club_grade`** |
| season_label | `single_line_text_field` | — |
| playhq_link | `url` | — |
| team_image | `file_reference` | — |
| sort_order | `number_integer` | — |
| featured | `boolean` | — |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> `club_team` là hub trung tâm — Player, Sponsor (gián tiếp), và Event đều reference qua đây.

---

