### 🎫 `membership_type` — Reference term + Product

| Field | Type | References → |
|---|---|---|
| title | `single_line_text_field` | — |
| **category** | `metaobject_reference` | → **`membership_category`** |
| description | `multi_line_text_field` | — |
| benefits | `rich_text_field` | — |
| eligibility | `multi_line_text_field` | — |
| **linked_product** | `product_reference` | → **Shopify Product** |
| badge | `file_reference` | — |
| sort_order | `number_integer` | — |

> [!TIP]
> `membership_type` kết nối metaobject ↔ product. Các loại như Life Member không cần product, chỉ dùng metaobject.

