## 3. Article Metafields (Events Blog)

Namespace: `event` — Owner: `ARTICLE`

| Field | Key | Type | References → |
|---|---|---|---|
| Event Start | `event.start_datetime` | `date_time` | — |
| Event End | `event.end_datetime` | `date_time` | — |
| Venue | `event.venue` | `single_line_text_field` | — |
| External Link | `event.external_link` | `url` | — |
| Button Label | `event.button_label` | `single_line_text_field` | — |
| Registration Deadline | `event.registration_deadline` | `date_time` | — |
| Event Type | `event.event_type` | `single_line_text_field` | — |
| Featured Event | `event.featured` | `boolean` | — |
| **Related Team** | `event.related_team` | `metaobject_reference` | → **`club_team`** |

---

## 4. Product Metafields (Membership Products)

Namespace: `membership` — Owner: `PRODUCT`

| Field | Key | Type |
|---|---|---|
| Season | `membership.season` | `single_line_text_field` |
| Eligibility | `membership.eligibility` | `multi_line_text_field` |
| Benefit Summary | `membership.benefit_summary` | `rich_text_field` |
| Renewal Note | `membership.renewal_note` | `multi_line_text_field` |

---

## 5. Tóm tắt tất cả References

Bảng tổng hợp mọi relationship trong hệ thống:

| Từ (Source) | Field | → Tới (Target) | Loại |
|---|---|---|---|
| `club_team` | sport | → `club_sport` | metaobject_reference |
| `club_team` | division | → `club_division` | metaobject_reference |
| `club_team` | grade | → `club_grade` | metaobject_reference |
| `player_profile` | team | → `club_team` | metaobject_reference |
| `club_sponsor` | scope | → `sponsor_scope` | metaobject_reference |
| `club_sponsor` | tier | → `sponsor_tier` | metaobject_reference |
| `club_sponsor` | sponsored_player | → `player_profile` | metaobject_reference |
| `club_person` | group | → `club_people_group` | metaobject_reference |
| `membership_type` | category | → `membership_category` | metaobject_reference |
| `membership_type` | linked_product | → **Product** | product_reference |
| Article (Events) | event.related_team | → `club_team` | metaobject_reference |

---

## 6. Chuỗi Reference (Reference Chains)

Các chuỗi relationship gián tiếp quan trọng:

```
🏈 Filter Player theo Sport:
   player_profile → club_team → club_sport

🏅 Filter Sponsor theo Sport (gián tiếp qua player):
   club_sponsor → player_profile → club_team → club_sport

📅 Filter Event theo Sport:
   Article (Event) → club_team → club_sport

🎫 Membership → Product:
   membership_type → Product (via linked_product)
   Product → membership.* metafields (season, eligibility, etc.)
```

---

## 7. Blogs & Collections

### Blogs
| Blog | Dùng cho | Template riêng | Metafields |
|---|---|---|---|
| **News** | Tin tức CLB | ✅ | Không |
| **Events** | Sự kiện | ✅ | 9 article metafields (`event.*`) |

### Collections đề xuất
| Collection | Loại | Mục đích |
|---|---|---|
| All Merchandise | Smart/Manual | Tất cả merch |
| All Memberships | Smart/Manual | Tất cả gói membership |
| Featured Merch | Smart | Sản phẩm nổi bật |
| Team Merch Football | Smart | Merch bóng đá |
| Team Merch Netball | Smart | Merch netball |
| Sale | Smart | Đang giảm giá |
| New Arrivals | Smart | Mới ra |
